name: SNIF Marketplace Access (SWEEP THE OTHER ONE FOR MOMENTUM ) (NOT THIS ONE)

metadata.name: SNIF Marketplace Pass
metadata.description:
A marketplace for SNIF holders which will be used to generate more charity donation funds and to act as a sink for NFT project based tokens (such as $JIRA, $SPIT, $BYTES, $SOS, etc.). All project tokens spent will be burned for the benefit of the entire space, and all ETH spent will be 100% added to the project funds - to be donated & distributed to artists.

Only SNIF Genesis holders & holders of these Marketplace Passes will be able to utilize the SNIF Marketplace.
